<h2>FAQ deep dives</h2>
<p><strong>When post-purchase cross-sell?</strong> After delivery +14 days bulky goods; day 14 consumables; never before customer has product for furniture. Stack operators should document this answer in internal runbooks — not rely on tribal knowledge when agencies turn over.</p>
<p><strong>Gift order handling?</strong> Separate branch — packaging/care for gift buyer, no recipient cross-sell to purchaser. Stack operators should document this answer in internal runbooks — not rely on tribal knowledge when agencies turn over.</p>
